{"tid":2076451,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"《蝙蝠俠：不敗之謎》導演 Joel Schumacher 病逝　終年 80 歲","createTime":"2020-06-23T13:41:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T13:12:15.000Z","uid":134683,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"440f45af88f44b53a8ec03cba47481ebc0a84624","tid":2076451,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T13:41:44.000Z","msg":"知名導演&nbsp;Joel Schumacher 昨日（22 日）於紐約因癌病逝，終年 80 歲。他曾執導電影《粗野少年族》（The Lost Boys）（1985）、《St.&nbsp;Elmo's Fire》（1985）、《蝙蝠俠：不敗之謎》（Batman Forever)（1995）&nbsp; 、《蝙蝠俠與羅賓》（Batman &amp; Robin）（1997）等。&nbsp;<br />\n死訊由&nbsp;Schumacher 經理人發聲明證實，指 Schumacher「已安詳逝去」。<br />\nSchumacher 進入電影圈前，在時裝界工作，曾為 Woody Allen 的電影擔任造型師。他的導演出道作是 1981年 由 Lily Tomlin主演的《The Incredible Shrinking Woman》。1995年，Schumacher 執導由方&middot;基墨（Val Edward Kilmer）主演的《蝙蝠俠：不敗之謎》，續集《蝙蝠俠與羅賓》同樣由他執導。惟《蝙蝠俠與羅賓》於1997年上映後劣評如潮。<br />\n2017年，Schumacher&nbsp; 受訪時表示，自己是世界上其中一位最幸運的人，「因我實現了夢想，這夢想比我所能想像得更大」。他說，「你知道，我只是一個雙親早逝的小孩，獨自成長於螢幕前。我希望可以講一些故事。」<br />\nSchumacher 亦曾執導電影《歌聲魅影》（The Phantom of the Opera）（2004）。女主角 Emmy Rossum 得知 Schumacher逝世後，亦在twitter發文哀悼，寫道：「得知Joel Schumache 去世，我流淚了。他是獨一無二的，他的創意、熱情、力量，深深影響著我的人生。」"},{"pid":"9bc88b09b6834d65f73be373b9239a4910782bca","tid":2076451,"uid":134683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T13:42:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/culture/%E8%9D%99%E8%9D%A0%E4%BF%A0-%E5%B0%8E%E6%BC%94-joel-schumacher-%E7%97%85%E9%80%9D-%E7%B5%82%E5%B9%B4-80-%E6%AD%B2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%25E8%259D%2599%25E8%259D%25A0%25E4%25BF%25A0-%25E5%25B0%258E%25E6%25BC%2594-joel-schumacher-%25E7%2597%2585%25E9%2580%259D-%25E7%25B5%2582%25E5%25B9%25B4-80-%25E6%25AD%25B2%2F&d=91nyg34XrGq4aGOua7i4JXO0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=9ddcb12f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%25E8%259D%2599%25E8%259D%25A0%25E4%25BF%25A0-%25E5%25B0%258E%25E6%25BC%2594-joel-schumacher-%25E7%2597%2585%25E9%2580%259D-%25E7%25B5%2582%25E5%25B9%25B4-80-%25E6%25AD%25B2%2F&h=bd158f67\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/culture/%E8%9D%99%E8%9D%A0%E4%BF%A0-%E5%B0%8E%E6%BC%94-joel-schumacher-%E7%97%85%E9%80%9D-%E7%B5%82%E5%B9%B4-80-%E6%AD%B2/</a>"},{"pid":"36ce69d22d5844d7bb9c4d711ba733eeb5182da4","tid":2076451,"uid":94828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T13:43:05.000Z","msg":"仆街頑皮狗"},{"pid":"ba6f094acf5456e64b785e4a9a6e98c18fc20afc","tid":2076451,"uid":134683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"36ce69d22d5844d7bb9c4d711ba733eeb5182da4","tid":2076451,"uid":94828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T13:43:05.000Z","msg":"仆街頑皮狗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T13:52:57.000Z","msg":"關咩事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7811b723ef6b202bdabdd8cf7391de7738e938cf","tid":2076451,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T14:13:37.000Z","msg":"冇人識？"},{"pid":"423e1a7179b38ece4b63786263bf45a388fc7745","tid":2076451,"uid":21873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T13:12:15.000Z","msg":"燈上燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yBT0XM3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyBT0XM3.png&h=2880883e&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}